review_blob: Drinks best when the Keg is fresh, It is a one hit wonder as none of the other beers at the brewery are even palatable at all. This beet is awesome and it perfectly balanced.
beer_name: Mac and Jacks African Amber Ale

review_blob: Good stuff. Nice nose. Coffee up front and pumkin in the back. Needs more bittering.
Best Pumpkin of the year so far if you like the spice. No head ad no Lacing. Great Ale!
